### Task 1.4-1.N: Continue TDD cycle for remaining features

**Pattern**: For each feature (hooks, NDJSON parsing, stall detection, etc.):
1. Write failing test (RED)
2. Verify failure is expected (Verify RED)
3. Write minimal code to pass (GREEN)
4. Verify test passes (Verify GREEN)
5. Refactor if needed (REFACTOR)

**Features to TDD**:
[x] `run_mux_turn()` basic execution with mocked subprocess
[x] Hook execution (before_run, after_run)
[x] NDJSON event parsing
[x] Stall detection
[x] Timeout handling
[x] Error handling (command not found)
[x] Token usage extraction

**Estimated**: 2 hours (cumulative across all TDD cycles)

